text: Verna Westwood (born 30 August 1955) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
